      "span_text": "Yadav et al. [CITATION_1] analyzed the genomic binding sites of the TF, and their promoter nucleosome occupancy and transcriptome profile data showed that TF binding to proximal promoters influenced target gene expression when coupled to nucleosome repositioning or when binding close to nucleosome binding sites, in most cases."
